"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-when-is-lin-yu-ting-fighting-olympics-2024-gold-medal-boxing-start-time-tv-today-b1175545.html\", \"text\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies. Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search. See our privacy policy for more information.  Sport|Olympics  Lin Yu-Tingis a big favourite as she goes up against Julia Szeremeta for Olympic gold in Paris tonight.  The Taiwanese boxer, likeImane Khelif, has faced accusations she should not be competing at theOlympicsafter claims from the International Boxing Association that she failed a gender eligibility test.  Lin, who has gold medals at the World Championships and Asian Games, eased past Esra Yildiz Kahraman in her semi-final and now has the chance to be crowned featherweight champion.  Poland's Szeremeta is her final opponent, and the 20-year-old has insisted she is full of belief that she can pull off an upset against Lin.  \\\"I am not afraid of anyone,\\\" Szeremeta said.  \\\"I do not feel respect. I go out and do my thing. I can not wait for the final.  Lin Yu-Ting takes on Julia Szeremeta in the women's featherweight gold-medal fight.  The gold-medal bout is scheduled for 8:30pm BST tonight, Saturday, August 10.  TV channel:In the UK, Imane Khelief's final will be shown on Eurosport and the BBC.  Live stream: Subscribers can visit the discovery+ |Paris 2024app and website to watch the fight in full, while you can also watch live online for free via the BBC Sport and BBC iPlayer.  Live blog: Follow live coverage of the fight withStandard Sport's rolling Olympics blog, with expert analysis from reporters Matt Majendie and Malik Ouzia in Paris.  MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\"}"